comments: I used the first three letters to identify the words and associate them with each object, then noticing which where similar (like SDE and SDI) to learn how to tell them apart. In the last part, I also used some of the three ending letters to choose one option over the over when the word showed up too fast and I didn't catch the first half. It was hard to make the associations at first because both the language and the objects were uncommon and not familiar.
